    <stitle>ELECTRICAL SYSTEM TROUBLESHOOTING GUIDE - 9800 - FULLER 10 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS - INSPECT - INPUT SHAFT
        SEAL
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="inspect" graphiccount="0">
        <title>INPUT SHAFT SEAL</title>
        <para>The input shaft seal is a mechanical seal system. Grooves or "threads" in the input shaft force oil
            rearward and back into the transmission as the shaft rotates. Inspect the input shaft grooves and the inside
            of the front bearing cover for damage. Replace any damaged parts.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
